BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Stockholm:20260325T180000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Stockholm:20260325T220000
SUMMARY:Play board games with Gothenburg Boardgamers - Open for everyone
DESCRIPTION:GoBo is a board game association for people of all ages and le
 vels of experience. We provide locales to play in and boardgames (over 500
  of them)\, have some snacks and drinks for sale and create different event
 s.\n\nWe're located on Gyllenkrooksgatan 5\, to the left of the main entra
 nce. Open every Wednesday 18–22 and every Saturday 12–22.\n\nVisiting us i
 s always completely free the first time. Afterwards you can become a member
  or pay a small fee each visit.\n\nFor more information: www.gothenburgboar
 dgamers.se
URL:https://www.meetup.com/gothenburg-board-gamers-gobo/events/313853691/
UID:event_313853691@meetup.com
LOCATION:Gyllenkrooksgatan 5\, Gothenburg\, Sweden
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
